node.text:
... we recently celebrated our 1 year Anniversary and to have so many friends and family attend & even travel to attend & celebrate our union and love was a blessing and a testament of who they are to us and who we are to them.... We are Blessed in love and family. May God continue to bless us and keep us as we proceed on this beautiful journey together as husband and wife. 

𝒯𝒽𝑒 𝒮𝒶𝓃𝓉𝒶𝓃𝒶’𝓈 
𝟨/𝟨/𝟤𝟢 ♾❤️♾

🎥 @lloydb.media
@joshdeanfilms

node.text:
NEVER did I think when I woke up today, I’d be typing RIP for my beautiful and ever so sweet Grandmother, Joan Davis❤️ • 😞Lord in heaven I try not to question your will but I can’t help but wonder why was today her day of all people. She is our family’s Matriarch, the glue, the calm, the root, the Queen of my late grandfather’s castle, the giver of life and light, the wisdom and the structure. Raising 7 children and a host of grandchildren and nieces and nephews, everyone AFFECTIONATELY called her “𝑴𝒂𝒎𝒂 “🙏🏼😞 How can she not be here to be all those things and more.🤦🏻‍♀️💔 

Please pray for my family 🙏🏼 and may you Rest In Peace with God forever 𝑴𝒂𝒎𝒂 • I love you ❤️ #JoanDavis
